9. Ben Burton extended the knot tables up to 19 crossings, it would be nice to have support for
its data: https://regina-normal.github.io/data.html

8. [DONE] The syntax <[generators]; [relators]> for a finitely presented group now allows
for the addition of selected elements: <[generators]; [relators]; [elements]> .
This is presently only used in printout of the representations and only for
the representations ks_S<n> ks_A<n> .

